title: Ritz to Present Free Lecture on Joint Replacement (Commonwealth Health)
text: ( Source : Commonwealth Health ) WILKES-BARRE, Pa. (Oct. 21, 2015 ) - George Ritz , M.D. , will present a lecture on joint replacement surgery at 6 p.m. Oct. 28 at the Keystone Grand Ballroom , Mohegan Sun Pocono, Plains Township. Sponsored by
